<p data-start="69" data-end="94">Te explico corto y claro:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="19zk934" data-start="96" data-end="110">❌ Problema</h3>
<p data-start="111" data-end="141">Ese link:<br>
👉 GitHub (<code data-start="132" data-end="138">.git</code>)</p>
<p data-start="143" data-end="254">No es un menú visible para clientes.<br data-start="179" data-end="182">
Es un repositorio (código), no una página para que la gente vea el menú.</p>
<hr data-start="256" data-end="259">
<h3 data-section-id="2hny1c" data-start="261" data-end="283">✅ Lo que necesitás</h3>
<p data-start="284" data-end="297">Un link tipo:</p>
<ul data-start="298" data-end="390">
<li data-section-id="5kifjt" data-start="298" data-end="329">
<p data-start="300" data-end="329">Página web (ej: GitHub Pages)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="jfpx7p" data-start="330" data-end="362">
<p data-start="332" data-end="362">Google Drive (archivo público)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lhq0qa" data-start="363" data-end="390">
<p data-start="365" data-end="390">O una web simple del menú</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="392" data-end="395">
<h3 data-section-id="11q2v7c" data-start="397" data-end="439">🔥 SOLUCIÓN RÁPIDA (la mejor para vos)</h3>
<p data-start="440" data-end="477">Ya que lo tenés en GitHub, hacé esto:</p>
<ol data-start="479" data-end="609">
<li data-section-id="1nygzjq" data-start="479" data-end="505">
<p data-start="482" data-end="505">Subí tu menú ahí (HTML)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hwnz90" data-start="506" data-end="532">
<p data-start="509" data-end="532">Activá <strong data-start="516" data-end="532">GitHub Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1q5c92r" data-start="533" data-end="609">
<p data-start="536" data-end="561">Te va a dar un link tipo:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="565" data-end="609"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 415px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://cafelulu.github.io/...</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="610" data-end="642">Ese <strong data-start="614" data-end="642">sí es el que va en el QR</strong></p>
<hr data-start="644" data-end="647">
<h3 data-section-id="15vbzc1" data-start="649" data-end="670">💡 Mientras tanto</h3>
<p data-start="671" data-end="700">Si querés, hago esto por vos:</p>
<p data-start="702" data-end="714">👉 Me decís:</p>
<ul data-start="715" data-end="737">
<li data-section-id="536siz" data-start="715" data-end="737">
<p data-start="717" data-end="737">“haceme el menú web”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="739" data-end="749">Y te armo:</p>
<ul data-start="750" data-end="815">
<li data-section-id="fcnzk" data-start="750" data-end="765">
<p data-start="752" data-end="765">El menú listo</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15grelv" data-start="766" data-end="787">
<p data-start="768" data-end="787">El link funcionando</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="127cz10" data-start="788" data-end="815">
<p data-start="790" data-end="815">El QR listo para imprimir</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="817" data-end="820">
<p data-start="822" data-end="890">Decime:<br>
👉 ¿Querés que use los precios que ya tenías de Café Lulù?</p>
<p data-start="892" data-end="940">Y en 1 mensaje te dejo TODO listo (menú + QR 🔥)</p>
