Es solo el repositorio de GitHub, yo no puedo convertirlo automáticamente en página pública sin que actives algo vos.</p>
<p data-start="175" data-end="272">👉 O sea: <strong data-start="185" data-end="238">no existe todavía un link “abrible” para clientes</strong>, por eso no tengo uno para darte.</p>
<hr data-start="274" data-end="277">
<h3 data-section-id="1pzg36v" data-start="279" data-end="325">💥 Te lo soluciono rápido (posta en 2 min)</h3>
<p data-start="327" data-end="337">Hacé esto:</p>
<ol data-start="339" data-end="547">
<li data-section-id="xjkcat" data-start="339" data-end="400">
<p data-start="342" data-end="400">Entrá a tu repo:<br data-start="358" data-end="361">
<a data-start="364" data-end="400" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://github.com/CafeLulu/Caf-Lul-">https://github.com/CafeLulu/Caf-Lul-<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8soadx" data-start="402" data-end="436">
<p data-start="405" data-end="436">Andá a:<br>
<strong data-start="416" data-end="436">Settings → Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6cbrmt" data-start="438" data-end="535">
<p data-start="441" data-end="535">En “Source” elegí:<br>
👉 <code data-start="466" data-end="488">Deploy from a branch</code><br data-start="488" data-end="491">
👉 Branch: <code data-start="505" data-end="511">main</code><br data-start="511" data-end="514">
👉 Folder: <code data-start="528" data-end="535">/root</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ogj5k8" data-start="537" data-end="547">
<p data-start="540" data-end="547">Guardás</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="549" data-end="552">
<h3 data-section-id="uki54m" data-start="554" data-end="574">✅ Después de eso</h3>
<p data-start="575" data-end="607">GitHub te va a dar un link tipo:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="608" data-end="652"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://cafelulu.github.io/Caf-Lul-/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="654" data-end="736">Ese es el que:<br>
✔ abre el menú<br data-start="683" data-end="686">
✔ sirve para clientes<br data-start="707" data-end="710">
✔ sirve para hacer el QR</p>
<hr data-start="738" data-end="741">
<h3 data-section-id="1dwcyw0" data-start="743" data-end="766">🚀 Cuando lo tengas</h3>
<p data-start="767" data-end="840">Pasámelo y te hago:<br>
👉 el QR listo para imprimir (te lo dejo como imagen)</p>
<hr data-start="842" data-end="845">
