<h2 data-section-id="1wwtwo0" data-start="168" data-end="201">🎨 DISEÑO (basado en tu carta)</h2>
<ul data-start="202" data-end="389">
<li data-section-id="1mlkycl" data-start="202" data-end="225">
<p data-start="204" data-end="225">Fondo azul oscuro ✔</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1omhhe4" data-start="226" data-end="251">
<p data-start="228" data-end="251">Detalles en naranja ✔</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8ycd03" data-start="252" data-end="304">
<p data-start="254" data-end="304">Tipografía elegante (igual vibe que tu imagen) ✔</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1y2tn9y" data-start="305" data-end="347">
<p data-start="307" data-end="347">Dibujitos estilo café (minimalistas) ✔</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="z2oxt8" data-start="348" data-end="389">
<p data-start="350" data-end="389">Título grande: <strong data-start="365" data-end="378">Café Lulù</strong> arriba ✔</p>
</li>
