<hr data-start="96" data-end="99">
<h1 data-section-id="14wz451" data-start="101" data-end="131">🚀 PASO 1 — Crear el archivo</h1>
<ol data-start="132" data-end="336">
<li data-section-id="1292jr6" data-start="132" data-end="157">
<p data-start="135" data-end="157">Abrí <strong data-start="140" data-end="157">Bloc de notas</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hqk1il" data-start="158" data-end="187">
<p data-start="161" data-end="187">Pegá el código que te pasé</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jfxw2r" data-start="188" data-end="222">
<p data-start="191" data-end="222">Tocá <strong data-start="196" data-end="222">Archivo → Guardar como</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="nq2gjf" data-start="223" data-end="261">
<p data-start="226" data-end="233">Nombre:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="237" data-end="261"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 415px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6my26a" data-start="262" data-end="307">
<p data-start="265" data-end="307">En “Tipo” poné:<br>
👉 <em data-start="287" data-end="307">Todos los archivos</em></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vblzmh" data-start="308" data-end="336">
<p data-start="311" data-end="336">Guardalo en el escritorio</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="338" data-end="341">
<h1 data-section-id="10ybrsp" data-start="343" data-end="373">🌐 PASO 2 — Subirlo a GitHub</h1>
<ol data-start="375" data-end="560">
<li data-section-id="1dr1utt" data-start="375" data-end="434">
<p data-start="378" data-end="434">Entrá a tu repo:<br>
👉 <a data-start="398" data-end="434" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://github.com/CafeLulu/Caf-Lul-">https://github.com/CafeLulu/Caf-Lul-<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10zjxze" data-start="436" data-end="484">
<p data-start="439" data-end="484">Tocá el botón:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="457" data-end="484">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ck7cg0" data-start="486" data-end="521">
<p data-start="489" data-end="521">Arrastrá el archivo <code data-start="509" data-end="521">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19zx3nb" data-start="523" data-end="560">
<p data-start="526" data-end="560">Bajá y tocá:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="542" data-end="560">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="562" data-end="565">
<h1 data-section-id="19ygfz2" data-start="567" data-end="615">⚙️ PASO 3 — Activar la página (MUY IMPORTANTE)</h1>
<ol data-start="617" data-end="703">
<li data-section-id="oxgwnx" data-start="617" data-end="651">
<p data-start="620" data-end="651">Arriba entrá a:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="639" data-end="651">Settings</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="dujy1m" data-start="653" data-end="680">
<p data-start="656" data-end="680">Bajá hasta:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="671" data-end="680">Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bbu61f" data-start="682" data-end="703">
<p data-start="685" data-end="703">En “Source” elegí:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<ul data-start="704" data-end="765">
<li data-section-id="1e73u5c" data-start="704" data-end="728">
<p data-start="706" data-end="728">Deploy from a branch</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6h02st" data-start="729" data-end="747">
<p data-start="731" data-end="747">Branch: <code data-start="739" data-end="745">main</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cgd099" data-start="748" data-end="765">
<p data-start="750" data-end="765">Folder: <code data-start="758" data-end="765">/root</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<ol start="4" data-start="767" data-end="783">
<li data-section-id="1w0ghyf" data-start="767" data-end="783">
<p data-start="770" data-end="783">Tocá <strong data-start="775" data-end="783">Save</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="785" data-end="788">
<h1 data-section-id="zdpqhf" data-start="790" data-end="818">⏳ PASO 4 — Esperar el link</h1>
<p data-start="820" data-end="852">Esperá 30 segundos – 1 minuto ⏱️</p>
<p data-start="854" data-end="880">Te va a aparecer algo así:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="881" data-end="925"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://cafelulu.github.io/Caf-Lul-/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="927" data-end="930">
<h1 data-section-id="1y1sv9v" data-start="932" data-end="951">✅ PASO 5 — Probar</h1>
<ul data-start="953" data-end="1003">
<li data-section-id="1bo97s9" data-start="953" data-end="970">
<p data-start="955" data-end="970">Entrá al link</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="pegbax" data-start="971" data-end="1003">
<p data-start="973" data-end="1003">Si ves tu menú → PERFECTO 🔥</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1005" data-end="1008">
<h1 data-section-id="1f63oqt" data-start="1010" data-end="1026">📲 PASO 6 — QR</h1>
<p data-start="1028" data-end="1066">Cuando tengas el link:<br>
👉 me lo mandás</p>
<p data-start="1068" data-end="1140">y te hago:<br>
✔ QR listo<br data-start="1089" data-end="1092">
✔ para imprimir<br data-start="1107" data-end="1110">
✔ para poner en mesas / caja</p>
<hr data-start="1142" data-end="1145">
<h1 data-section-id="15yf606" data-start="1147" data-end="1170">💥 EXTRA (IMPORTANTE)</h1>
<p data-start="1171" data-end="1198">Si no te aparece la página:</p>
<ul data-start="1199" data-end="1249">
<li data-section-id="xa367z" data-start="1199" data-end="1209">
<p data-start="1201" data-end="1209">refrescá</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10me1gu" data-start="1210" data-end="1249">
<p data-start="1212" data-end="1249">o esperá 2 min (GitHub tarda a veces)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1251" data-end="1254">
<p data-start="1256" data-end="1313">Si te trabás en algún paso decime:<br>
