</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="250" data-end="283">👉 Click en <strong data-start="262" data-end="283">Create repository</strong></p>
<hr data-start="285" data-end="288">
<h2 data-section-id="woagk" data-start="290" data-end="335">✅ 2. Crear el menú (esto es lo importante)</h2>
<p data-start="337" data-end="405">Cuando entres al repo nuevo, vas a ver una pantalla con pocas cosas.</p>
<p data-start="407" data-end="487">👉 Buscá y tocá:<br>
<strong data-start="424" data-end="445">“Create new file”</strong> (está en el medio de la pantalla, grande)</p>
<hr data-start="489" data-end="492">
<h2 data-section-id="1vz2sgx" data-start="494" data-end="520">✅ 3. Nombre del archivo</h2>
<p data-start="522" data-end="537">Arriba escribí:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="538" data-end="556"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="558" data-end="561">
<h2 data-section-id="1ylwexh" data-start="563" data-end="585">✅ 4. Pegá el código</h2>
<p data-start="587" data-end="620">Pegá TODO el menú que te di antes</p>
<hr data-start="622" data-end="625">
<h2 data-section-id="134xpp" data-start="627" data-end="642">✅ 5. Guardar</h2>
<p data-start="644" data-end="681">Abajo del todo:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="663" data-end="681">Commit changes</strong></p>
<hr data-start="683" data-end="686">
<h2 data-section-id="3oq8sf" data-start="688" data-end="710">✅ 6. Activar la web</h2>
<ol data-start="712" data-end="798">
<li data-section-id="oxgwnx" data-start="712" data-end="746">
<p data-start="715" data-end="746">Arriba entrá a:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="734" data-end="746">Settings</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="dujy1m" data-start="748" data-end="775">
<p data-start="751" data-end="775">Bajá hasta:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="766" data-end="775">Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bbu61f" data-start="777" data-end="798">
<p data-start="780" data-end="798">En “Source” elegí:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<ul data-start="799" data-end="842">
<li data-section-id="1e73u5c" data-start="799" data-end="823">
<p data-start="801" data-end="823">Deploy from a branch</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="157rb37" data-start="824" data-end="832">
<p data-start="826" data-end="832">main</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="189fzdt" data-start="833" data-end="842">
<p data-start="835" data-end="842">/root</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="844" data-end="851">👉 Save</p>
<hr data-start="853" data-end="856">
<h2 data-section-id="e2bwod" data-start="858" data-end="873">⏳ 7. Esperar</h2>
<p data-start="875" data-end="890">Esperá 1 minuto</p>
<p data-start="892" data-end="919">Te va a aparecer algo como:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="920" data-end="969"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://cafelulu.github.io/cafelulu-menu/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="971" data-end="974">
<h2 data-section-id="aoiaqv" data-start="976" data-end="990">🔥 8. FINAL</h2>
<p data-start="992" data-end="1032">Entrá al link<br data-start="1005" data-end="1008">
Si ves el menú → listo</p>
<p data-start="1034" data-end="1070">👉 Me lo mandás<br data-start="1049" data-end="1052">
y te hago el QR 🔥</p>
<hr data-start="1072" data-end="1075">
<p data-start="1077" data-end="1171" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">💬 Si no ves <strong data-start="1090" data-end="1111">“Create new file”</strong>, mandame captura YA<br data-start="1131" data-end="1134">
