<hr data-start="68" data-end="71">
<h1 data-section-id="6zkhtk" data-start="73" data-end="104">⚙️ PASO 6 — ACTIVAR LA PÁGINA</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="15jipud" data-start="106" data-end="128">📍 1. Ir a Settings</h2>
<p data-start="129" data-end="179">Dentro de tu repo (donde subiste el <code data-start="165" data-end="177">index.html</code>):</p>
<p data-start="181" data-end="212">Arriba vas a ver pestañas como:</p>
<ul data-start="213" data-end="270">
<li data-section-id="1uweazp" data-start="213" data-end="221">
<p data-start="215" data-end="221">Code</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sztk2" data-start="222" data-end="232">
<p data-start="224" data-end="232">Issues</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="518brj" data-start="233" data-end="250">
<p data-start="235" data-end="250">Pull requests</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="hwee3f" data-start="251" data-end="270">
<p data-start="253" data-end="270"><strong data-start="253" data-end="265">Settings</strong> ⚙️</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="272" data-end="292">👉 Tocá <strong data-start="280" data-end="292">Settings</strong></p>
<hr data-start="294" data-end="297">
<h2 data-section-id="hatrng" data-start="299" data-end="322">📍 2. Buscar “Pages”</h2>
<p data-start="323" data-end="347">Ahora estás en Settings.</p>
<p data-start="349" data-end="412">👉 Bajá un poco (lado izquierdo o centro)<br data-start="390" data-end="393">
👉 Buscá: <strong data-start="403" data-end="412">Pages</strong></p>
<p data-start="414" data-end="488">(Si no lo ves, decime y te digo exactamente dónde mirar según tu pantalla)</p>
<hr data-start="490" data-end="493">
<h2 data-section-id="my3dzq" data-start="495" data-end="514">📍 3. Configurar</h2>
<p data-start="515" data-end="543">Ahí vas a ver algo que dice:</p>
<p data-start="545" data-end="558">👉 <strong data-start="548" data-end="558">Source</strong></p>
<p data-start="560" data-end="573">Cambiá eso a:</p>
<ul data-start="575" data-end="636">
<li data-section-id="1e73u5c" data-start="575" data-end="599">
<p data-start="577" data-end="599">Deploy from a branch</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6h02st" data-start="600" data-end="618">
<p data-start="602" data-end="618">Branch: <code data-start="610" data-end="616">main</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cgd099" data-start="619" data-end="636">
<p data-start="621" data-end="636">Folder: <code data-start="629" data-end="636">/root</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="638" data-end="641">
<h2 data-section-id="1v97fkp" data-start="643" data-end="659">📍 4. Guardar</h2>
<p data-start="660" data-end="676">👉 Tocá <strong data-start="668" data-end="676">Save</strong></p>
<hr data-start="678" data-end="681">
<h2 data-section-id="1wwda7j" data-start="683" data-end="698">⏳ 5. Esperar</h2>
<p data-start="699" data-end="728">Esperá 30 segundos a 1 minuto</p>
<p data-start="730" data-end="766">Y arriba te va a aparecer algo tipo:</p>
<p data-start="768" data-end="807">👉 “Your site is live at…” + un link 🔥</p>
<hr data-start="809" data-end="812">
<h2 data-section-id="97l2ou" data-start="814" data-end="828">📲 6. Final</h2>
<p data-start="829" data-end="857">Entrás al link → ves tu menú</p>
<p data-start="859" data-end="911">👉 Me lo pasás<br data-start="873" data-end="876">
y te hago el QR listo para imprimir</p>
<hr data-start="913" data-end="916">
