La <strong data-start="46" data-end="73">opción 3 (sistema real)</strong> ya es nivel “negocio digital”, pero te la explico clara sin humo.</p>
<hr data-start="141" data-end="144">
<h1 data-section-id="1dey6fp" data-start="146" data-end="171">🧠 ¿QUÉ ES LA OPCIÓN 3?</h1>
<p data-start="172" data-end="261">👉 Que el cliente haga el pedido<br data-start="204" data-end="207">
👉 Y a vos te llegue SOLO en una pantalla (sin hablar)</p>
<p data-start="263" data-end="271">Ejemplo:</p>
<ul data-start="272" data-end="393">
<li data-section-id="er4ukm" data-start="272" data-end="297">
<p data-start="274" data-end="297">Cliente escanea QR 📲</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hshbq5" data-start="298" data-end="317">
<p data-start="300" data-end="317">Elige productos</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="hg450k" data-start="318" data-end="342">
<p data-start="320" data-end="342">Toca “Enviar pedido”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o7112l" data-start="343" data-end="393">
<p data-start="345" data-end="393">Vos lo ves en una tablet/PC en el mostrador 💻</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="395" data-end="398">
<h1 data-section-id="14kz9en" data-start="400" data-end="419">⚙️ ¿QUÉ NECESITA?</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1yjvvl7" data-start="421" data-end="449">1. FRONTEND (ya lo tenés)</h2>
<p data-start="450" data-end="502">👉 Tu menú (lo que hicimos)<br data-start="477" data-end="480">
Eso es la parte visual</p>
<hr data-start="504" data-end="507">
<h2 data-section-id="7voanw" data-start="509" data-end="538">2. BACKEND (lo importante)</h2>
<p data-start="539" data-end="573">👉 Un “cerebro” que reciba pedidos</p>
<p data-start="575" data-end="584">Ejemplos:</p>
<ul data-start="585" data-end="649">
<li data-section-id="tv11vj" data-start="585" data-end="596">
<p data-start="587" data-end="596">Node.js</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="bdtam6" data-start="597" data-end="636">
<p data-start="599" data-end="636">Firebase (MUY recomendado para vos)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="2io2a2" data-start="637" data-end="649">
<p data-start="639" data-end="649">Supabase</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="651" data-end="688">👉 Este guarda pedidos en tiempo real</p>
<hr data-start="690" data-end="693">
<h2 data-section-id="1x3iokh" data-start="695" data-end="714">3. BASE DE DATOS</h2>
<p data-start="715" data-end="746">👉 Donde se guardan los pedidos</p>
<p data-start="748" data-end="756">Ejemplo:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="757" data-end="851"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Pedido 1:</span><br><span>- Café con leche x2</span><br><span>- Medialuna x1</span><br><span>Total: 5000</span><br><span>Estado: pendiente</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="853" data-end="856">
<h2 data-section-id="1vjsmrl" data-start="858" data-end="878">4. PANEL PARA VOS</h2>
<p data-start="879" data-end="909">👉 Una pantalla donde ves todo</p>
<p data-start="911" data-end="916">Tipo:</p>
