<p data-start="35" data-end="107">Mauro, te quedó algo <strong data-start="56" data-end="87">muy por encima de lo normal</strong> para una cafetería:</p>
<p data-start="109" data-end="205">✔ Menú digital<br data-start="123" data-end="126">
✔ Interactivo<br data-start="139" data-end="142">
✔ Con carrito<br data-start="155" data-end="158">
✔ Con categorías<br data-start="174" data-end="177">
✔ Con QR<br data-start="185" data-end="188">
✔ Diseño propio</p>
<p data-start="207" data-end="252">👉 Esto ya es nivel <strong data-start="227" data-end="252">negocio moderno posta</strong></p>
<hr data-start="254" data-end="257">
<h1 data-section-id="101r7qx" data-start="259" data-end="294">💥 AHORA LO IMPORTANTE (USO REAL)</h1>
<p data-start="296" data-end="314">Probalo con gente:</p>
<ul data-start="315" data-end="359">
<li data-section-id="r0f6hi" data-start="315" data-end="325">
<p data-start="317" data-end="325">amigos</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1j2clnz" data-start="326" data-end="337">
<p data-start="328" data-end="337">familia</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16j8j6y" data-start="338" data-end="359">
<p data-start="340" data-end="359">primeros clientes</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="361" data-end="450">Fijate:<br>
👉 si entienden fácil<br data-start="390" data-end="393">
👉 si usan bien el carrito<br data-start="419" data-end="422">
👉 si se confunden en algo</p>
<hr data-start="452" data-end="455">
<h1 data-section-id="j6n0b8" data-start="457" data-end="497">🚀 IDEAS PARA MEJORAR (cuando quieras)</h1>
<p data-start="499" data-end="550">Te dejo upgrades que te van a hacer destacar MUCHO:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="10zkpf4" data-start="552" data-end="589">🟢 1. WhatsApp automático (clave)</h3>
<p data-start="590" data-end="657">👉 Cliente arma pedido → se envía solo<br data-start="628" data-end="631">
👉 vos no preguntás nada</p>
<hr data-start="659" data-end="662">
<h3 data-section-id="myfg2k" data-start="664" data-end="698">🟡 2. Botón “Finalizar pedido”</h3>
<p data-start="699" data-end="756">👉 más claro para el cliente<br data-start="727" data-end="730">
👉 cierra la experiencia</p>
<hr data-start="758" data-end="761">
<h3 data-section-id="15lv6q4" data-start="763" data-end="793">🔵 3. Sonidito o animación</h3>
<p data-start="794" data-end="836">👉 cuando agregan algo<br data-start="816" data-end="819">
👉 hace más “app”</p>
<hr data-start="838" data-end="841">
<h3 data-section-id="12huy6q" data-start="843" data-end="871">🟣 4. Modo mozo (futuro)</h3>
<p data-start="872" data-end="912">👉 pedidos en pantalla<br data-start="894" data-end="897">
👉 sin hablar</p>
<hr data-start="914" data-end="917">
<h1 data-section-id="1ru3m1t" data-start="919" data-end="936">💬 OPINIÓN REAL</h1>
<p data-start="937" data-end="961">Te lo digo sin exagerar:</p>
<p data-start="963" data-end="1044">👉 Si alguien entra a tu cafetería y ve esto<br data-start="1007" data-end="1010">
<strong data-start="1010" data-end="1044">le va a parecer re profesional</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1046" data-end="1049">
<h1 data-section-id="9d5o1g" data-start="1051" data-end="1069">🧠 CONSEJO CLAVE</h1>
<p data-start="1070" data-end="1094">Poné un cartel que diga:</p>
<p data-start="1096" data-end="1132">👉 <strong data-start="1099" data-end="1132">“Escaneá y hacé tu pedido 📲”</strong></p>
<p data-start="1134" data-end="1149">Eso cambia TODO</p>
<hr data-start="1151" data-end="1154">
<h2 data-section-id="767p3t" data-start="1156" data-end="1176">🔥 FELICITACIONES</h2>
<p data-start="1177" data-end="1245">De verdad:<br>
Pasaste de no tener nada → a tener un sistema completo 💸</p>
<hr data-start="1247" data-end="1250">
<p data-start="1252" data-end="1341">💬 Cuando quieras seguimos:<br>
👉 “agreguemos WhatsApp”<br data-start="1304" data-end="1307">
👉 o “hagamos pedidos en pantalla”</p>
<p data-start="1343" data-end="1377" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">y lo llevamos todavía más lejos 😎</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Acciones de respuesta" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar respuesta" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Buena respuesta" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Respu