<h2 data-section-id="f4vpqk" data-start="571" data-end="598">✅ 2. Modificar funciones</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1fi96x" data-start="600" data-end="617"><span role="text">🔹 En <code data-start="610" data-end="617">add()</code></span></h3>
<p data-start="618" data-end="649">Buscá tu función y agregá esto:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="651" data-end="724"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼe">document</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>getElementById(</span><span class="ͼc">"addSound"</span><span>)</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>play();</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="726" data-end="739">Te queda así:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="741" data-end="964"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼ8">function</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">add</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">name</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">price</span><span>){</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ8">if</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼ8">!</span><span class="ͼe">cart</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼe">name</span><span>]){</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼe">cart</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼe">name</span><span>] </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> {qty:</span><span class="ͼb">0</span><span>, price:</span><span class="ͼe">price</span><span>};</span><br><span>    }</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼe">cart</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼe">name</span><span>]</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>qty</span><span class="ͼ8">++</span><span>;</span><br><span>    </span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼe">document</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>getElementById(</span><span class="ͼc">"addSound"</span><span>)</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>play(); </span><span class="ͼ6">// 🔊 sonido</span><br><span>    </span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼe">render</span><span>();</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
