<hr data-start="968" data-end="971">
<h1 data-section-id="1amesmp" data-start="973" data-end="995">⚠️ 4. MUY IMPORTANTE</h1>
<p data-start="996" data-end="1008">Probalo así:</p>
<ul data-start="1009" data-end="1079">
<li data-section-id="xn3k64" data-start="1009" data-end="1079">
<p data-start="1011" data-end="1079">Tocá el botón ➕<br data-start="1026" data-end="1029">
👉 el sonido SOLO se activa cuando hay interacción</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1081" data-end="1084">
<h1 data-section-id="1k5s1xh" data-start="1086" data-end="1102">🧪 TEST RÁPIDO</h1>
<p data-start="1103" data-end="1130">Probá esto en tu navegador:</p>
<ol data-start="1132" data-end="1223">
<li data-section-id="9cxxln" data-start="1132" data-end="1151">
<p data-start="1135" data-end="1151">Abrí la página</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17ozq0l" data-start="1152" data-end="1163">
<p data-start="1155" data-end="1163">Tocá ➕</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9n4ftz" data-start="1164" data-end="1223">
<p data-start="1167" data-end="1223">Si no suena → apretá F12 (consola) y fijate si hay error</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1225" data-end="1228">
<h1 data-section-id="adzw4t" data-start="1230" data-end="1254">💥 SI TODAVÍA NO SUENA</h1>
<p data-start="1255" data-end="1265">Puede ser:</p>
<ul data-start="1266" data-end="1331">
<li data-section-id="w9vc5c" data-start="1266" data-end="1287">
<p data-start="1268" data-end="1287">el audio no carga</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="14l1jgv" data-start="1288" data-end="1304">
<p data-start="1290" data-end="1304">GitHub tarda</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="18wjup8" data-start="1305" data-end="1331">
<p data-start="1307" data-end="1331">o el navegador bloquea</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1333" data-end="1397">👉 En ese caso decime:<br>
<strong data-start="1356" data-end="1397">“pasame versión que funcione sí o sí”</strong></p>
<p data-start="1399" data-end="1443">y te doy un código con sonido garantizado 🔥</p>
<hr data-start="1445" data-end="1448">
<p data-start="1450" data-end="1494" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Tranqui que esto lo hacemos sonar sí o sí 😎</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Acciones de respuesta" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copiar respuesta" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Buena respuesta" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-la