(esto pasa mucho con audios online en GitHub Pages)</p>
<hr data-start="122" data-end="125">
<h1 data-section-id="1k2d5f2" data-start="127" data-end="145">💥 PROBLEMA REAL</h1>
<p data-start="146" data-end="185">👉 Los links de audio externos a veces:</p>
<ul data-start="186" data-end="257">
<li data-section-id="16qz8d" data-start="186" data-end="201">
<p data-start="188" data-end="201">no cargan ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="14bm4z3" data-start="202" data-end="222">
<p data-start="204" data-end="222">son bloqueados ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="13tcqq5" data-start="223" data-end="257">
<p data-start="225" data-end="257">o GitHub no los permite bien ❌</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="259" data-end="262">
<h1 data-section-id="12ztmet" data-start="264" data-end="307">✅ SOLUCIÓN DEFINITIVA (LA QUE USAN TODOS)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1t97q8x" data-start="309" data-end="350">🔊 USAR AUDIO LOCAL (esto nunca falla)</h2>
<hr data-start="352" data-end="355">
<h2 data-section-id="16jxfs5" data-start="357" data-end="389">🚀 PASO 1 — Descargar sonidos</h2>
<p data-start="391" data-end="406">Descargá estos:</p>
<p data-start="408" data-end="484">👉 Sonido agregar:<br data-start="426" data-end="429">
<a data-start="429" data-end="482" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://www.soundjay.com/buttons/sounds/button-09.mp3<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<p data-start="486" data-end="561">👉 Sonido quitar:<br data-start="503" data-end="506">
<a data-start="506" data-end="559" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://www.soundjay.com/buttons/sounds/button-10.mp3<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<hr data-start="563" data-end="566">
<h2 data-section-id="lynck9" data-start="568" data-end="600">📁 PASO 2 — Subirlos a GitHub</h2>
<ol data-start="602" data-end="710">
<li data-section-id="1ws3x2c" data-start="602" data-end="659">
<p data-start="605" data-end="659">Entrá a tu repo<br data-start="620" data-end="623">
👉 <a data-start="626" data-end="659" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://github.com/CafeLulu/menu-<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xzn77r" data-start="661" data-end="700">
<p data-start="664" data-end="700">Tocá:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="673" data-end="700">Add file → Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="132n5cb" data-start="702" data-end="710">
<p data-start="705" data-end="710">Subí:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<ul data-start="711" data-end="739">
<li data-section-id="ztxd2h" data-start="711" data-end="724">
<p data-start="713" data-end="724"><code data-start="713" data-end="722">add.mp3</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1192qha" data-start="725" data-end="739">
<p data-start="727" data-end="739"><code data-start="727" data-end="739">remove.mp3</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<ol start="4" data-start="741" data-end="762">
<li data-section-id="n98kqj" data-start="741" data-end="762">
<p data-start="744" data-end="762"><strong data-start="744" data-end="762">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="764" data-end="767">
